data.description: Welcome to this inviting porch-front twin home, flooded with natural light. You'll find a spacious custom kitchen, perfect for cooking and gatherings. Upstairs, there are three decent-sized bedrooms and a full bath.  Convenience is key with main floor laundry and a powder room. Recent upgrades include a new heater and hot water system.  Located on a great block, you'll appreciate the friendly neighborhood and its proximity to all the shopping on Ridge Ave.  Schedule a viewing today to see if this home suits your needs.
